{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_017SW82t4D3c7pbMmcNbz5Qk","type":"tool_result","content":"# Image References and Asset Paths in Stellaclaw Documentation\n\nBased on the provided webpage content, here are all identified image and asset references:\n\n## Image Files Referenced\n\n1. **Stellacode Desktop Screenshot**\n   - Path: `docs/assets/stellacode.png`\n   - Context: \"Stellacode desktop connected to a server workspace\"\n\n2. **Telegram Groups Diagram**\n   - Path: `docs/assets/telegram.png`\n   - Context: \"Telegram groups backed by the same Stellaclaw server\"\n\n3. **SSHFS Remote Workspace Illustration**\n   - Path: `docs/assets/remote-sshfs-illusion.svg`\n   - Context: Demonstrates how remote mode creates an illusion of local workspace operations backed by remote servers\n\n4. **Two-Hop Remote Access Diagram**\n   - Path: `docs/assets/remote-web-two-hop.svg`\n   - Context: Shows \"Two-hop remote access through Stellacode and Web Channel\"\n\n## Asset Directory Structure\n\nAll images are stored in the `docs/assets/` directory, using both PNG and SVG formats for different visualization needs."}]},"parent_tool_use_id":"toolu_01WryJS6GgGE1XbrKuZD9cNw","session_id":"9df2fcc9-2a5f-4ef3-89ac-b9c468cf2a48","uuid":"4c1521bb-15a6-4d85-bc5c-da69f93711ec","timestamp":"2026-05-07T22:39:13.757Z"}
